sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validation Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as trainer-controller-manager<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod (rank 0)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant TrainingPods as Training Pods (all ranks)<br/>29500/TCP TCP

    Note over User, TrainingPods: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed / Denied
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch TrainJob resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: TrainJob event (Added/Modified)

    Controller->>Controller: Resolve TrainingRuntime/<br/>ClusterTrainingRuntime reference

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: JobSet created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (RHOAI)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: NetworkPolicy created

    opt Gang Scheduling Enabled
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup<br/>(coscheduling or Volcano)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    opt MPI ML Policy
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create SSH Secret + Hostfile ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update TrainJob status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch JobSet, create Jobs/Pods
    K8sAPI-->>JobSetCtrl: JobSet reconciled

    Note over User, TrainingPods: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking (RHOAI)

    loop Every 30s (configurable RequeueAfter)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List pods for TrainJob<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list (find rank-0)
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy enforced)
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: JSON training status<br/>(steps, epochs, loss)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch TrainJob annotations<br/>with progress data<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    Note over User, TrainingPods: Flow 3: PyTorch Distributed Training (inter-pod)

    TrainingPods->>TrainingPods: Rendezvous: rank-0 master<br/>29500/TCP<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy: same-job)
    TrainingPods->>TrainingPods: NCCL/gloo collective ops<br/>Dynamic ports TCP/UDP<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy: same-job)
